      <img height="155" width="557" alt="Rewarding and Inspiring Great Teaching Since 1983" src="/public/images/reward_and_inspire.jpg"> 
      <p class="intro"> <strong>The Presidential Awards for Excellence in Mathematics and Science Teaching (PAEMST)</strong> are the nation's highest honors for teachers of mathematics and science (including computer science). Awardees serve as models for their colleagues, inspiration to their communities, and leaders in the improvement of mathematics and science education. </p> 
      <p class="intro"> Since 1983, more than 4,300 teachers have been recognized for their contributions in the classroom and to their profession. If you know great teachers, nominate them to join this prestigious network of professionals. </p> 
      <div class="hr_dashed"> 
      </div> 
